OL,3,C'I've been a bit low profile': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham scores goals at charity match
OL,6,FMayor of Greater Manchester Andy
OL,7,FBurnham joked with the crowd at
OL,8,Ffootball match as speculation mounts
OL,9,Fon whether he'll challenge the Prime
OL,10,FMinister's leadership
OL,12,FAndy Burnham's movements are being
OL,13,Fclosely watched amid speculation of a
OL,14,Fleadership challenge, following the
OL,15,FLabour Party's disastrous showing in
OL,16,Fthe local elections.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
