PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778501468
OL,3,C'I've been a bit low profile': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham scores goals at charity match
OL,6,FThe results, which saw the party lose
OL,7,Fhundreds of councillors, mainly to
OL,8,FReform UK, has prompted a number of
OL,9,FLabour MPs to call on the Prime
OL,10,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer to quit.
OL,12,FThe Mayor of Greater Manchester is
OL,13,Fwidely viewed as a potential
OL,14,Fchallenger for the leadership, but has
OL,15,Fnot yet commented on the results.
OL,17,FHe pulled out of an event on Friday
OL,18,Fmorning, May 8, in Manchester, where
OL,19,Fhe was due to make a speech at the
OL,20,Fsecond annual Festival of Childhood.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
