OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778501468
OL,3,C'I've been a bit low profile': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham scores goals at charity match
OL,6,FHe did, however, stick to plans of
OL,7,Fplaying in a charity football match
OL,8,Ffor a homeless charity.
OL,10,FThe Mayor celebrated after scoring a
OL,11,Fgoal for Booth Centre FC in their
OL,12,Fcharity match
OL,14,FAhead of the game, Mr Burnham teased
OL,15,Fthe crowd and said: "I'm grateful to
OL,16,Fyou.
OL,18,F"You've probably seen I've been a bit
OL,19,Flow profile recently...so I thought I
OL,20,Fneeded something to, you know, lift up
OL,21,Fthe attention a bit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778501468
OL,3,C'I've been a bit low profile': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham scores goals at charity match
OL,6,FThe Mayor went on: "Because I'm still
OL,7,Ftrying to get to the highest
OL,8,Flevel...I'm hoping to attract the
OL,9,Fattention of David Moyes tonight."
OL,11,FMr Burnham, who is an Everton FC fan,
OL,12,Fthen went on to score two goals for
OL,13,Fthe charity team, Booth Centre FC.
OL,15,FZoe Muldoon reports as Andy Burnham
OL,16,Fmakes first public appearance
OL,17,Ffollowing the Labour Party's huge
OL,18,Flosses in the local elections
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
