OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778501468
OL,3,C'I've been a bit low profile': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham scores goals at charity match
OL,6,FThere have been murmurs suggesting
OL,7,Fthat Mr Burnham does intend to return
OL,8,Fto Westminster, and has ambitions to
OL,9,Fchallenge the Prime Minister for the
OL,10,Fleadership.
OL,12,FHowever, earlier this year, his path
OL,13,Fback to Westminster was blocked by
OL,14,FLabour's ruling national executive
OL,15,Fcommittee.
OL,17,FHe was blocked from standing in the
OL,18,FGorton and Denton by-election after
OL,19,Fprevious MP Andrew Gwynne stepped down
OL,20,Ffor health reasons.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
