OL,3,C'I've been a bit low profile': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham scores goals at charity match
OL,6,FA number of North West Labour MPs have
OL,7,Fcome out in support of Mr Burnham.
OL,9,FCrewe and Nantwich MP Connor Naismith
OL,10,Fsaid: "Andy is the most popular Labour
OL,11,Fpolitician in the country.
OL,13,F"The suggestion that he wouldn't be
OL,14,Fable to win in some of the seats
OL,15,FLabour is currently struggling to win
OL,16,Fis just wrong.
OL,18,F"Ironically, this is precisely why we
OL,19,Fneed him back on the front line of
OL,20,Fnational politics."
OL,26,@rD@GOUuD@AOUzD@AOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
