PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778501468
OL,3,C'I've been a bit low profile': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham scores goals at charity match
OL,6,FLucy Powell, the Manchester Central MP
OL,7,Fand deputy leader of the Labour Party
OL,8,Fsaid Mr Burnham was "very popular and
OL,9,Fhe's a great asset to the Labour
OL,10,FParty" and "I want to see us using all
OL,11,Fof the talents that we have".
OL,13,FBut she added: "I don't want to see a
OL,14,Fleadership challenge, that's not how
OL,15,Fwe operate in the Labour Party... We
OL,16,Fdon't do hostile takeovers in the
OL,17,FLabour Party, it's not what we're
OL,18,Fabout, it's not what people want to
OL,19,Fsee, it's not what our members want to
OL,20,Fsee."
OL,26,@pD@UOUrD@FO]rD@LOUsD@\O]uD@POU|D@EO]
